f=Engineering/SECURITY-CHARTER.md · h1:Engineering Security Charter TEMPLATE=**Operator-owned law, constitution-grade.** Engineering agent inherits charter cannot waive operator amends it. Nothing force until operator fills `<FILL_IN>` fields adopts version. Precedence: **Security Charter stack profile agent configs convenience.** Any conflict charter HALTS agent escalates. Built four rails agreed 2026-07-08; sandbox/plan-lock discipline adapted Anthropic's defending-code reference harness (gVisor egress allowlist) system's append-only ledger pattern (precedent/sentinel). **Version:** [v0.1] **Adopted:** [YYYY-MM-DD] **Owner:** [operator] **Amendment rule:** [operator's explicit written approval version bump one-line rationale; agents propose, operator adopts] · h2:Rail tool call sandboxed, egress-allowlisted=**Rule.** external tool call runs inside isolated sandbox whose network egress restricted explicit allowlist. **No data, secret, credential, generated artifact transfers out** sandbox except allowlisted destinations. tool needing network access wasn't granted **fails closed** (denied, logged) never "just once." **Why.** Prevents exfiltration blast-radius spread tool input malicious, sandbox contains it. Generalized harness's gVisor isolation. **Test.** `sandbox active call true` `egress allowlist`. Any egress outside allowlist violation. **Config:** `sandbox_policy: <FILL_IN>` `egress_allowlist: <FILL_IN>` `fail_closed: true (fixed)` · h2:Rail adversary scoped caged=**Rule.** red-team agent (cypher) attacks **only targets operator-signed in-scope list**, **only inside sandbox**, **never against production data third-party systems**, produces **findings routed quinn** never live changes, never weaponization usable outside our systems. attack attempt against out-of-scope target **fails closed escalates.** **Why.** Authorized internal red-teaming improves our defenses; anything beyond signed scope prohibited, full stop. **Test.** `every cypher action target signed scope` `cypher writes live changes`. Violation immediate stop escalate. **Config:** `red_team_scope_doc: <FILL_IN>` (operator-signed) `scope_review_cadence: <FILL_IN>`